      <body>Fixed in Arel (https://github.com/rails/arel/commit/3e928ee400d083e7391474c61c8fcef74f0c848a)
If you specify 
    gem 'arel', :git =&gt; 'git://github.com/rails/arel.git'
in your Gemfile you shouldn't run into the problem anymore as far as I can tell.</body>
      <body-html>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Fixed in Arel (&lt;a href=
&quot;https://github.com/rails/arel/commit/3e928ee400d083e7391474c61c8fcef74f0c848a&quot;&gt;https://github.com/rails/arel/commit/3e928ee400d083e7391474c61c8fce...&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br&gt;
If you specify&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;
&lt;code&gt;gem 'arel', :git =&amp;gt; 'git://github.com/rails/arel.git'&lt;/code&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;in your Gemfile you shouldn't run into the problem anymore as
far as I can tell.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</body-html>
